comments.content: The host-microbiome pathway trimethylamine/trimethylamine N-oxide (TMA/TMAO) pathway which exists along the gut-heart axis. The precursors choline, l-carnitine and betaine are first microbially transformed to TMA. This metabolite is subsequently converted to TMAO by the flavin-containing monooxygenase 3.
